	S_ISVTX from one file to another.  Fall back to fchmod/chmod when
	acls are unsupported.
	(set_acl): Add: set a file's acl and S_ISUID, S_ISGID, and
	S_ISVTX to a defined value.  Fall back to fchmod/chmod when acls
	are unsupported.

